12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><a href=\"https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/description/5420/\">https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/description/5420/</a></p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"过部分样例的一个题解\"><a href=\"#过部分样例的一个题解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"过部分样例的一个题解\"></a>过部分样例的一个题解</h1><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br><span class=\"line\">79</span><br><span class=\"line\">80</span><br><span class=\"line\">81</span><br><span class=\"line\">82</span><br><span class=\"line\">83</span><br><span class=\"line\">84</span><br><span class=\"line\">85</span><br><span class=\"line\">86</span><br><span class=\"line\">87</span><br><span class=\"line\">88</span><br><span class=\"line\">89</span><br><span class=\"line\">90</span><br><span class=\"line\">91</span><br><span class=\"line\">92</span><br><span class=\"line\">93</span><br><span class=\"line\">94</span><br><span class=\"line\">95</span><br><span class=\"line\">96</span><br><span class=\"line\">97</span><br><span class=\"line\">98</span><br><span class=\"line\">99</span><br><span class=\"line\">100</span><br><span class=\"line\">101</span><br><span class=\"line\">102</span><br><span class=\"line\">103</span><br><span class=\"line\">104</span><br><span class=\"line\">105</span><br><span class=\"line\">106</span><br><span class=\"line\">107</span><br><span class=\"line\">108</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"keyword\">include</span><span class=\"string\">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"keyword\">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> n,m,all,value[<span class=\"number\">2010</span>],parent[<span class=\"number\">2010</span>],childvalue[<span class=\"number\">2010</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">bool</span> deleted[<span class=\"number\">2010</span>];<span class=\"comment\">//true表示被删除，false表示可用，memset(deleted,false,sizeof(deleted))重置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt; children[<span class=\"number\">2010</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">bool</span> <span class=\"title\">subtree</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> root,<span class=\"type\">int</span> target)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> curr = target;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(curr)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(curr == root) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        curr = parent[curr];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">childdelete</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(deleted[i]) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    deleted[i] = <span class=\"literal\">true</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">auto</span> it:children[i]) <span class=\"built_in\">childdelete</span>(it);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">otherdelete</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> current,<span class=\"type\">int</span> target)</span></span>&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//删除除了target和其后代之外的所有节点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(target==<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(current == target) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    deleted[current]=<span class=\"literal\">true</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">auto</span> it : children[current])&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">otherdelete</span>(it,target);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">valuecompute</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(deleted[i]) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(children[i].<span class=\"built_in\">empty</span>())&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        childvalue[i] = value[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> childvalue[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    childvalue[i] = value[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">auto</span> it:children[i])&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(!deleted[it]) childvalue[i] += <span class=\"built_in\">valuecompute</span>(it);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> childvalue[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">count</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> cnt = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(!deleted[i]) cnt+=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> cnt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">query</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//计算所有的delta,并返回当前最小的那个</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> minval = <span class=\"number\">1e9</span><span class=\"number\">+10</span> , mindown = <span class=\"number\">2010</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(deleted[i]) <span class=\"keyword\">continue</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> delta = <span class=\"built_in\">abs</span>(all - <span class=\"number\">2</span>*childvalue[i]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(delta &lt; minval)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            minval = delta;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            mindown = i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>((delta == minval)&amp;&amp;(i&lt;mindown)) mindown = i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> mindown;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt; <span class=\"title\">tofinal</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> k)</span></span>&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//询问k</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt; ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> current_root = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">count</span>()&gt;<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> t = <span class=\"built_in\">query</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ans.<span class=\"built_in\">push_back</span>(t);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">subtree</span>(t,k))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">otherdelete</span>(current_root,t);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            current_root = t;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            all = <span class=\"built_in\">valuecompute</span>(current_root);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">childdelete</span>(t);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            all = <span class=\"built_in\">valuecompute</span>(current_root);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    cin &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        cin &gt;&gt; value[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">2</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> t ;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        cin &gt;&gt; t;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        parent[i] = t;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        children[t].<span class=\"built_in\">push_back</span>(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"type\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&lt;=m;i++)&#123; </span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">memset</span>(deleted,<span class=\"literal\">false</span>,<span class=\"built_in\">sizeof</span>(deleted));</span><br><span class=\"line\">        all = <span class=\"built_in\">valuecompute</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> num;cin&gt;&gt;num;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        vector&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt; ans = <span class=\"built_in\">tofinal</span>(num);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">auto</span> it:ans) cout &lt;&lt; it &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">&#x27; &#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        cout &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">&#x27;\\n&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"一些技巧\"><a href=\"#一些技巧\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一些技巧\"></a>一些技巧</h1><ol>\n<li>在一个图中，如果要删除某些节点，除了直接将节点下标丢掉、delete掉对应指针之外，还可以<strong>另外维护一个标记，用以表示’该节点被删除’，并在功能函数中访问该标记</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"错误总结\"><a href=\"#错误总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"错误总结\"></a>错误总结</h1><h2 id=\"基础错误\"><a href=\"#基础错误\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基础错误\"></a>基础错误</h2><ol>\n<li>函数名、变量名打错</li>\n<li>等号<code>==</code>写成赋值符号<code>=</code></li>\n<li>忘记使用abs绝对值</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"逻辑错误\"><a href=\"#逻辑错误\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"逻辑错误\"></a>逻辑错误</h2><ol>\n<li><p>在valuecompute函数中，累加子节点前<code>for(auto it:children[i]){ ... }</code>应该先重置权值，即应该先执行<code>childvalue[i] = value[i];</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>query函数遍历寻找最小的下标时，应该注意访问delete下标</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>递归函数，比如childdelete函数，应该使用递归删除的模式，不然就会只删除一层</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>明确所写的函数的功能，不要加入无关、错误的语句</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>分清楚要处理的遍历。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>在tofinal函数中，最后分支语句调用两个删除函数时，应该注意传入的参数是tofinal内定义的临时变量，而不是给tofinal传入的变量k.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>涉及状态重置的，一律<strong>先重置，再处理数据</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>删除逻辑：<br> 在树有关的题目中，所写到的函数有一部分是需要固定<code>传入根节点下标作为参数</code>的。但是，当出现删除函数，并且根节点被删除了，这类函数会出现失效<br> 因此，在调用时，可能需要设置一个<code>虚拟根节点</code>，用来标记当根节点被删除之后、当前位置最高的节点下标，并给上面那类函数传入该坐标，防止无法继续运行。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>在做题时，这里的all表示<code>当前所有节点的权值</code>，它一开始只是query函数里的一个临时变量。每次使用都会调用valuecompute函数（这也是某些节点被删除之后必要的，用于更新节点所有后代的权值和）。</li>\n<li>但是，我很快发现，如果根节点被删除了，那么，调用valuecompute函数应该从哪里开始调用起？而作为query函数内部临时变量的all是没办法解决这个问题的，毕竟再给query函数加入一个参数作为<code>本次询问中的虚拟根节点</code>会很麻烦</li>\n<li>因此，我把all变成了全局变量，并且将<code>虚拟根节点</code>和<code>valuecompute函数的调用</code>放到了tofinal函数中，这样就避免了<code>根节点被删除</code>从而无法使用valuecompute函数更新childvalue数组的情况</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"数据结构误用\"><a href=\"#数据结构误用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"数据结构误用\"></a>数据结构误用</h2><p>题目逻辑中，有一个关于<code>节点t是否在节点k的子树中</code>的判断，一开始使用并查集处理，但是发现这最终会把<code>每个节点所处的树</code>这一信息压缩成<code>每个节点的祖先</code>。<br>    - 最后，写了一个subtree函数用来辅助判断</p>\n<h1 id=\"时间复杂度分析及代码改进\"><a href=\"#时间复杂度分析及代码改进\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"时间复杂度分析及代码改进\"></a>时间复杂度分析及代码改进</h1>","feature":true,"text":"题目链接 https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/description/5420/ 过部分样例的一个题解12345678...","permalink":"/post/第32次CCFCSP T3树上搜索","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"算法","slug":"算法","count":16,"path":"api/categories/算法.json"},{"name":"做题记录","slug":"算法/做题记录","count":4,"path":"api/categories/算法/做题记录.json"}],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目链接</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BF%87%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%A0%B7%E4%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">过部分样例的一个题解</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一些技巧</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">错误总结</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基础错误</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">逻辑错误</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E8%AF%AF%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">数据结构误用</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%8F%8A%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">时间复杂度分析及代码改进</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"LHY","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/256316666?s=400&u=531212165de7b7b90dc6ec2dd44404fc88f4a435&v=4","link":"/","description":"天空中的宝石应该交由天空去寻找","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"梯度求解：树与字符串","uid":"974692d18caa4f14235f9193c4f5cb5e","slug":"梯度求解：树、字符串","date":"2026-03-09T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-03-10T12:02:53.934Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/梯度求解：树、字符串.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"题目链接 题解1234567891011121314151617181920212223242526272829303132333435363738394041...","permalink":"/post/梯度求解：树、字符串","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.9k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"DFS","slug":"DFS","count":6,"path":"api/tags/DFS.json"}],"author":{"name":"LHY","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/256316666?s=400&u=531212165de7b7b90dc6ec2dd44404fc88f4a435&v=4","link":"/","description":"天空中的宝石应该交由天空去寻找","socials":{"github